WHEREAS, the members and coaches of the Pleasant View 6U All-Stars baseball team
have etched their names into the annals of Tennessee sports history; their dedication,
determination, work ethic, and talent not only made possible a successful and memorable
baseball season but also surely point toward their success in all future endeavors; now,
therefore,
BE IT RESOLVED BY THE HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES OF THE ONE HUNDRED
FOURTEENTH GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE, THE SENATE
CONCURRING, that we honor and congratulate the members and coaches of the Pleasant
View 6U All-Stars baseball team on winning the 2024 Dixie Youth Baseball World Series.
BE IT FURTHER RESOLVED, that an appropriate copy of this resolution be prepared
for presentation with this final clause omitted from such copy and upon proper request made to
the appropriate clerk, the language appearing immediately following the State seal appear
without House or Senate designation.
